# Simulation V2 contract, source controls, and quarantine metadata are small,
# auditable source artifacts and must remain versioned.
!data/simulation_contract_v2/
!data/simulation_contract_v2/**
!data/PGDA_SYNTH_DATASET_V2/
!data/PGDA_SYNTH_DATASET_V2/README.md
